item.title: Hard (Feat Kry) - Tome [Experimental RNB]
item.dc:creator: iammane
item.description:
I fixed up your title a bit

This is awesome! I really like it, is the singing you? The vocals fit the vibe very well.

Great job, I’ll have to give a listen on better 'phones later the bass sounds a little muddy but I don’t fault you, I think it’s my work headset.

EDIT:
Third or so listen on better headphones, the bass is a little muddy. I think just lowering the volume a bit, or maybe a little bit of high pass just to take the bite off.

Otherwise, this is LIT AF. This is really good.
